<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>NC Score Activation Email</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
</head>

<body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 0; min-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: #FAFAFA; color: #222222;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div style=" padding: 24px; color: #0070f3; text-align: center;">
            <img src="cid:logo" alt="NC Score Logo" style="display: block; margin: 15px auto; max-width: 150px;" />
            <h1
                style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.25; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: center;">
                Welcome to NC Score</h1>
            <hr style="border: 1px solid #0070f3; margin: 20px 0;" />
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 24px; background-color: #ffffff;">
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Hello {{name}},</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">	
            Bạn hoặc một ai đó đã sử dụng chức năng quên mật khẩu. Nếu bạn muốn đặt lại mật khẩu thì nhấn vào link bên dưới và làm theo hướng dẫn.</p>
            <h2
                style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.25; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: center;">
                {{resetLink}}</h2>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Please enter this code on the activation page within the next
                1 minutes.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">If you did not register for a NC Score account, please
                ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color: #f6f6f6; padding: 24px;">
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact
                us at <a href="https://www.facebook.com/KoPhaiVu" target="_blank"
                    style="color: #000; text-decoration:none;">@KoPhaiVu @Sukem
                </a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>